<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/fourways_logo.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
    <title>
        <%= seo?.title || 'About - Fourways' %>
    </title>
    <meta name="description" content="<%= seo?.description || 'About Fourways Coffee Roasters.' %>">
    <link rel="canonical" href="<%= seo?.canonicalUrl %>">
    <meta name="robots" content="<%= seo?.robots || 'index,follow' %>">
    <link href="/styles/home.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/styles/navbar.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/styles/cart.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/styles/footer.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&family=Comfortaa:wght@300..700&family=Roboto:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <script type="module" src="/scripts/home.js" defer></script>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
        <main class="page-wrapper">

            <div class="header__container">
                <h1 class="headline-text">About Fourways Coffee Roasters</h1>
            </div>
            <p class="text-light">Fourways is a nano-roastery. It is owned and operated by a single person - Matthew
                - and all coffee
                is roasted in micro batches. As a child, Matthew spend his summers at Fourways; his grandparents
                farm
                in
                County Antrim. His grandmother was a baker and grandfather a welder - both professions
                combine
                artistry, technical skill, and machinery to create things for people. Matthew sees his love of
                coffee
                roasting as a continuation of this family tradition and a way to find meaning and community in the
                present through connecting with his past.</p>

            <div class="header__container">
                <h2 class="headline-text">Shipping</h2>
            </div>
            <p class="text-light">Currently there is only one shipping option available - Royal Mail 48hrs tracked and
                is a fixed price
                of £3.55
                up to 2kg. Shipping options will be expanded in the future but for now it helps keeps operations
                manageable.</p>
            <div class="header__container">
                <h2 class="headline-text">Sizes</h2>
            </div>
            <p class="text-light">All bags are 250g. 1kg options are coming soon!</p>


            <div class="header__container">
                <h2 class="headline-text">Contact</h2>
            </div>
            <p class="text-light">You can reach out by email at <a class="success-email__link"
                    href="mailto:orders@fourways.coffee">orders@fourways.coffee</a> or through our <a
                    class="success-email__link" href="https://www.instagram.com/fourwayscoffee"
                    target="_blank">Instagram</a>
                page where you can also keep up to date on new releases, events,
                and news.</p>

            <% if (!isWebstoreInMaintenance) { %>
                <%- include('cart') %>
                    <div id="cart-overlay" class="cart-overlay"></div>
                    <% } %>
        </main>
        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>